%h3.heading-medium{ id: 'colour-contrast'} Colour contrast
%p.text The colour contrast ratio for text and interactive elements should be at least 4.5:1 <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20/visual-audio-contrast-contrast.html" rel="external">as recommended by the W3C</a>. Test your service to meet this standard.

%h3.heading-medium{ id: 'colour-sass-variables'} Sass variables
%p.text     Use Sass variables in case colour values need to be updated &ndash; find these in the GOV.UK frontend toolkit <a href="https://github.com/alphagov/govuk_frontend_toolkit/blob/master/stylesheets/_colours.scss" rel="external">colours.scss</a> file.

